comment: /**  * Return whether this BeanWiringInfo indicates autowiring.  */
code: /**  * Return whether this BeanWiringInfo indicates autowiring.  */ public boolean indicatesAutowiring() {     return (this.beanName == null). }

comment: /**  * Return the specific bean name that this BeanWiringInfo points to, if any.  */
code: /**  * Return the specific bean name that this BeanWiringInfo points to, if any.  */ @Nullable public String getBeanName() {     return this.beanName. }

comment: /**  * Return whether the specific bean name is a suggested default bean name,  * not necessarily matching an actual bean definition in the factory.  */
code: /**  * Return whether the specific bean name is a suggested default bean name,  * not necessarily matching an actual bean definition in the factory.  */ public boolean isDefaultBeanName() {     return this.isDefaultBeanName. }

comment: /**  * Return one of the constants {@link #AUTOWIRE_BY_NAME} /  * {@link #AUTOWIRE_BY_TYPE}, if autowiring is indicated.  */
code: /**  * Return one of the constants {@link #AUTOWIRE_BY_NAME} /  * {@link #AUTOWIRE_BY_TYPE}, if autowiring is indicated.  */ public int getAutowireMode() {     return this.autowireMode. }

comment: /**  * Return whether to perform a dependency check for object references  * in the bean instance (after autowiring).  */
code: /**  * Return whether to perform a dependency check for object references  * in the bean instance (after autowiring).  */ public boolean getDependencyCheck() {     return this.dependencyCheck. }
